{"tid":1836632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有武漢旅客表示打算經深圳轉車到香港探親！","createTime":"2020-01-23T09:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T09:34:33.000Z","uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0b7f60efbd8ec9cae94407ab5c177294779f6e","tid":1836632,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />OH NO"},{"pid":"dedf0f89928643a8ecaaebe1473c47b2e035061e","tid":1836632,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vYYm1qj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvYYm1qj.png&h=afc140ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=377855&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377855%26refer%3DShare&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=a5d10f41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377855%26refer%3DShare&h=78a80cb8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=377855&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"5f2aa726196082ac2beab7805e29cda95ec5af74","tid":1836632,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:27:40.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】不少乘客趕在武漢高鐵關閉離境通道前離開，部分人下午陸續抵達深圳，有武漢乘客透露，計劃去香港探親。<br />\n<br />\n在深圳北站，中午過後，由武漢開出的列車陸續到站，乘客都戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n由武漢乘高鐵去深圳車程要約五小時，有武漢居民透露，下一站計劃去香港。<br />\n<br />\n有婆婆帶同孫，由武漢回深圳探親。<br />\n<br />\n由武漢出發的高鐵，在早上十點鐘停運前有約17班開往深圳北站，不少乘客會選擇這個大站，再轉駁高鐵去其他地方，當中去香港的高鐵車程只需少於20分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n由深圳開往武漢的高鐵服務如常，但只會落客，不會上客。乘客指會在中途站下車， 但因為同車會有武漢人，都做好防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n高鐵站內大部分乘客都戴上口罩，多處都放置消毒酒精，而在高鐵站外，一批穿着全身防護裝備的人員，用儀器在四周噴灑消毒噴霧。"},{"pid":"902644b3d522c41dedc70708e717feae9db0b253","tid":1836632,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"探你老母"},{"pid":"1c0788511676fd85c357ed786b8a1e438f1ddfea","tid":1836632,"uid":283975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:28:54.000Z","msg":"驚死走來香港&hellip;真是pk"},{"pid":"1a14a24dd545e75163cf52c724520bc7ffbf069b","tid":1836632,"uid":150185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"同我死撚番去武漢"},{"pid":"3bc00a2da93ad4115327fd90d8fd7f076620517d","tid":1836632,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:29:08.000Z","msg":"交通工具好方便<br />\n<br />\n只要去到深圳北 四五個關口慢慢過都冇事"},{"pid":"d343e4e8770c4be596de714abeea258093f266af","tid":1836632,"uid":139199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bb170624b17b846dac927166006b13a4587d1c","tid":1836632,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zt6ovhy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZt6ovhy.png&h=30991610&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19e166a651c961aa7675ef4260f507fdb66af1f0","tid":1836632,"uid":236075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:33:06.000Z","msg":"真。攬炒，學下野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1055399922cac155db3fb830fb17c1964cc79c5","tid":1836632,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01bb170624b17b846dac927166006b13a4587d1c","tid":1836632,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zt6ovhy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZt6ovhy.png&h=30991610&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim